Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take this cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there is a rumor that a suspicious guy is walking around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I succeeded getting this one filmed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to trace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How does this sound, Atom? Would you investigate this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, You Three Second-Rate Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the map, it should be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It freaked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't use the searchlight since it stands out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a perfect place for a suspicious one to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't we be able to hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What, it's just a water sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? I heard some kind of construction sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. It's all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who is it?! -This is Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom? This is not a place for someone like you to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here after tracing the suspicious person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,who has been appearing near towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let me tell you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those suspicious ones are robots here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We got abandoned by humans and yet we missed our hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that we went out to hang out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tragedy of robots made by human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive those who abandoned robots so willfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get back at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Move. You'll get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't harm a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, how is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, Atom's a good robot. Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to remain stuck to your department!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, an intelligent robot like you wouldn't understand our rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot isn't a disposable machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo! Pitato! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. Pitato, let's get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lili. It's us who you've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the fire fighter robot Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the welder robot Pitato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We were abandoned a few days ago, and we missed where humans live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we visited there every night. Of course, the boss was angry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss? Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss was very kind to us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back at humans? We can't do that! We told him it's too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you said you were abandoned. Because of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But only once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us just made one mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As a nurse at a residence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was serving my ill mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of that robot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, it's time for you to take medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Lili.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you pick some flowers there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Would two or three be good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, please cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a fire fighter of a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I even used to get several recognitions for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than sprinkling water from outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to sprinkle water right in the burning place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened? Water isn't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how I got kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was working in a welding shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bit embarrassing for me to tell you, but I was a skillful welder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Pitato, so we don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a brand new welder robot. Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one stubborn salesperson, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pitato. You are doing it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pitato! Please park my car outside there under the streetlamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sir! Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a new robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's our brochure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However! We aren't outdated yet. We are still skillful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can work for a longer time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But we got abandoned
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and were transported
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to junkyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hell for us robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would humans abandon us so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For real. If they are careful about it, they could use us for a longer period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But they just change it to a new robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You will all get your energy removed and be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come you all! Those who can still move, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be a scrap metal, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boss must have also been abandoned like you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys going to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on?...What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean what we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we do get out, people will send us back to junkyard again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can still work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of... Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Of course! -For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There still must be places where robots are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But would people be able to recognize our ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... There might be some people who can recognize our ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show people that you guys can work greatly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We should do that for robots like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see. -Should we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that all three of you want to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Look, isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We all built it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Its name is Hopping Plane. -Hopping Plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let me fly it. -It's a fun thing to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Atom, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's all solved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Atom. Hurry and come back to report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is... I have this thing and I can't go back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There are abandoned robots here. So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? -I'll tell you once I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop! Step! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a country of jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Look at that! -That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how the country of construction should look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This view looks a bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Developing places would look like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Would we be able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? We are not the bad ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's defeat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Woo. If we leave it like this, someone will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the sultan of this island. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We are looking for some jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have tons of jobs here. Would you like to work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh? You guys are robots? -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-You are, you are, and you are, too! -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them here are robots except me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be jealous! You are a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's only for someone with some kind of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of them here have great abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I give shots, everything gets well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lili, do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is great. Great. Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can weld anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! This is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an excellent fire fighter. I can put out anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! This is the smallest volcano in the world! It's our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Sultan, this was bit too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but can't you see how skillful they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hire all three of them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I acknowledge your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hire all three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I object!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm the sultan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like what I do, then get out of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn your registration cards in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire fighter robot Woo. His registration has been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welder robot Pitato. This robot's registration has been cancelled as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots without registration cards are meant to be disassembled
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as they are discovered. Even the sultan cannot probably do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Don't be too tough on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose them! Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, cheer up. Even without registration cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Let's go to Cosmopolis. There should be some work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Cosmopolis? -It's an independent space country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,An independent space country? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Kids, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the Cosmopolis interception force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have invaded our territorial sky. If you don't get out, we'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not anyone suspicious. We are here to look for jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are robots. Do you guys have registration cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We will ask you one last time. This is the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have registration cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even get a chance to beg!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo! Run! I'll take care of the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet at the K point of the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't work now. We will get disassembled for not having registration cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you all safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all finished now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? Even for robots like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any place where we are needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there were, we don't have registration cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, there's a trouble. There has been an accident at the space factory 1022.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A meteor hit the factory and there was an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A rescue team was dispatched, but you should be faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry! -All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a goodbye, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You are coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lili, Woo, Pitato, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You will help me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fire accident site of the space factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The right wing of the factory is falling off from the main building with fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many people working in this factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Another minor explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait any longer for the rescue team!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it? A rescue team?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we are not. We are just scrap metals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A quite damaged vehicle is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo, please put that fire off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lili, help the injured ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitato, let's repair the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Would we be able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it! We will show them we can work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? They approached the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They are getting off one by one. It seems like they are robots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the rescue team here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. It's all over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, I'm leaving it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like a hose! It's running up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's rescuing the injured ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Go and help the injured ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lili!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one is heading to the right wing of the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't that Woo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How brave! He's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's putting the right wing back to the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's welding it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...? It's another meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on there. It's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. Who are these robots?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The rescue team is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You are late! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job! We'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. They are reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They are from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's pressing on as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire is off! Finally! It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's all right now. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lili! Lili!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Robot Junkyard" Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Robot Recycling Factory"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lili, Pitato, Woo. Thanks all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bit old, but it's still usable. Atom, I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Can I really take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it precious forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious beam that destroys the planetary probe and the space station.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The League of Nations have decided that it's done by Atlas, and dispatched a strong defense force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that Atlas fights a hard battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, a massive spaceship has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would this scary enemy be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Astro Boy vs. Atlas IX"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Astro Boy vs. Atlas IX"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.23,0:23:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:24:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
